Interface Taplytics.TaplyticsCodeExperimentListener

Taplytics
public static interface Taplytics.TaplyticsCodeExperimentListener

Interface for a Taplytics code experiment, one of the baselineVariation(Map) or experimentVariation(String, Map) methods will be called only once.
